{{wiktionarypar|klutz}}

A '''klutz''' is person who is clumsy, foolish, inept, or accident-prone.  The term is perhaps derived from the [[Yiddish]] &#1511;&#1500;&#64303;&#1509; ''klots'' ('wooden beam'), cognate with the  [[German language|German]] ''klotz'', meaning a "block" or "lump".

